{"id":5985,"date":"2024-02-24T17:12:33","date_gmt":"2020-02-24T11:42:33","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=5985"},"modified":"2024-10-28T20:11:58","modified_gmt":"2024-10-28T14:41:58","slug":"designer-wardrobe-ideas","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/designer-wardrobe-ideas\/","title":{"rendered":"Want A Modern Chamber? Pick From These Designer Wardrobe Ideas!"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><em>Make your bedroom modern with our flawless designer wardrobe picks.<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Imagine a bedroom without a wardrobe! You simply cannot, right? Well, that\u2019s how important it is, even when you are dreaming. Not just a functional piece of furniture, a wardrobe is also an aesthetic focal point of your bedroom. Along with their utility, wardrobes are also a significant component of decor and you can get a designer wardrobe that strikes a balance of both in your bedroom. Here is a list of designer wardrobes built with the latest materials, texture and patterns just for you!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Quintessentially Tasteful: Patterned Wardrobe<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Patterns can redefine the way we look at designer wardrobes. With detailed engravings or sleek cut-outs, a patterned wardrobe can provide a visual relief to plainly designed <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/bedroom-design\/\">bedroom interiors<\/a>. From floral to abstract, you can choose from a plethora of patterns and motifs for your designer wardrobe. This is one is an absolutely unique design and will definitely appeal to your minimalistic sensibilities as well.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005757\/patterned-designer-wardrobe.jpg\" alt=\"A patterned wardrobe plethora of patterns and motifs for your designer wardrobe\" class=\"wp-image-5986\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005757\/patterned-designer-wardrobe.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005757\/patterned-designer-wardrobe-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005757\/patterned-designer-wardrobe-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005757\/patterned-designer-wardrobe-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A patterned wardrobe helps you create a rich and textured bedroom<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Embrace a clutter free life with functional wardrobe designs\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/16114642\/clutter-free-life-with-functional-wardrobe-designs.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Chic Choice: Mirrors On Your Wardrobe<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Are you looking for a classy and functional designer wardrobe? There is a simple solution to it. Add a mirror! Smartly integrated to save space, mirrored wardrobes are multi-functional and amp up the aesthetics in one go. This wardrobe is perfect to deal with the design challenges of a small bedroom. Moreover, it also makes your chamber look and feel more spacious.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005800\/designer-wardrobe-with-mirrors.jpg\" alt=\"Top designer wardrobes with mirrors on wardrobe are the trending designer wardrobes\" class=\"wp-image-5987\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005800\/designer-wardrobe-with-mirrors.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005800\/designer-wardrobe-with-mirrors-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005800\/designer-wardrobe-with-mirrors-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005800\/designer-wardrobe-with-mirrors-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">For small bedrooms and even spacious ones,  mirrored wardrobes are trending due to its multi-purpose<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Also, Read About <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/wardrobe-design-dressing-table-mirror\/\">Wardrobe Designs With A Dressing Table And Mirror<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Smartly Streamlined: Walls To Utilise Wardrobes<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A great design choice for studio apartments, this wardrobe utilises most of the wall space. It is also stylish and lends a clean seamless look to your bedroom. You can <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/wardrobe-design-for-bedroom\/\">design a wardrobe<\/a> around a love-seat or near your bed. Either way, a wall-full wardrobe makes for a seamless and trendy bedroom any day!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005804\/wallcovering-designer-wardrobes.jpg\" alt=\"A great designer wardrobes to utilises most of the wall space to make a trendy bedroom designer wardrobes\" class=\"wp-image-5988\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005804\/wallcovering-designer-wardrobes.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005804\/wallcovering-designer-wardrobes-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005804\/wallcovering-designer-wardrobes-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005804\/wallcovering-designer-wardrobes-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Wallcovering wardrobes are stylish and utilitarian, do consider it for your designer wardrobe plan<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<iframe title=\"Latest Wardrobe Designs for Bedroom | 10 Best Wardrobe Design Ideas | Sliding Wardrobe Design\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" src=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/qXAglK-T_D8?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen><\/iframe>\n<\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Truly Trendy: Translucent Wardrobe<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Swept with style and statement, a translucent wardrobe is here to stay for eons. They are great to subtly show off your designer couture and yet not reveal it all. For quintessentially <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/modern-bedroom-designs\/\">modern bedroom interiors<\/a>, a translucent wardrobe is the right choice. You can choose various colours and textures to complement the palette of your bedroom and create something stunning!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005808\/translucent-designer-wardrobe.jpg\" alt=\"Translucent designer wardrobe is the right choice for storage and style option for your modern bedroom\" class=\"wp-image-5989\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005808\/translucent-designer-wardrobe.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005808\/translucent-designer-wardrobe-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005808\/translucent-designer-wardrobe-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005808\/translucent-designer-wardrobe-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Translucent wardrobe makes for an excellent storage and style option for your modern bedroom<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get a Free Modular Kitchen Worth \u20b92 Lakhs with Your Home Interiors.\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/08183703\/designcafe-offer-free-modular-kitchen-worth-2-lakhs.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Fully Fabulous: Fiber Panel Wardrobe<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>With natural tones, textures, fiber panelled wardrobes have quickly become everyone\u2019s preferred choice when it comes to designer wardrobes. Furthermore, the best part about these wardrobes is that they are light in weight. You can choose your designer fiber panelled wardrobe by picking from a wide range of textures, finishes, and colours and be spoilt for choice. Go for this wardrobe if style and simplicity are always your decor benchmarks!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005812\/fiber-panel-designer-wardrobe.jpg\" alt=\"Designer fiber panelled wardrobe by picking from a wide range of textures, finishes and colours\" class=\"wp-image-5990\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005812\/fiber-panel-designer-wardrobe.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005812\/fiber-panel-designer-wardrobe-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005812\/fiber-panel-designer-wardrobe-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005812\/fiber-panel-designer-wardrobe-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Fiber panel makes for great designer wardrobes with their streamlined and stunning look<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Smoothly Sorted: Sliding Wardrobe<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Sleek, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/sliding-wardrobe-design-ideas\/\">sliding wardrobes<\/a> always get you compliments. Design and function-wise, they are a smart designer wardrobe idea to rely on! For small bedrooms or studio apartments, these wardrobes are ideal if you are looking for space-saving storage units. You can choose plain colours or jazz it up with some iconic patterns&nbsp; and make it a great focal point of your bedroom!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005816\/sliding-designer-wardrobe.jpg\" alt=\"Sliding designer wardrobes for small bedrooms and apartments is a space saving storage designer wardrobe ideas\" class=\"wp-image-5991\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005816\/sliding-designer-wardrobe.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005816\/sliding-designer-wardrobe-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005816\/sliding-designer-wardrobe-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005816\/sliding-designer-wardrobe-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Looking for space-saving storage ideas? Count on sliding wardrobe designs<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Wonderfully Worked: Wooden Wardrobe<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Durable, minimalistic and functional, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/wooden-wardrobe-design-ideas\/\">wooden wardrobes<\/a> never go out of style. These types of designer wardrobes complement all colour palettes and enhance the look of your bedroom through refreshing contrast. Opt for laminate or solid wood &#8211; both work wonderfully well.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005819\/wooden-designer-wardrobes.jpg\" alt=\"Wooden designer wardrobe build by laminate or solid wood materials for every type of bedroom interior design\" class=\"wp-image-5992\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005819\/wooden-designer-wardrobes.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005819\/wooden-designer-wardrobes-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005819\/wooden-designer-wardrobes-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005819\/wooden-designer-wardrobes-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Wooden wardrobes are sophisticated and great for almost every type of bedroom interior design<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Basic And Brilliant: Built-In Wardrobe<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Both for the sake of convenience and design, a built-in wardrobe is great. They not only make optimum use of space but look absolutely stunning and chic too. So whether you own a modern or vintage styled bedroom, built-in wardrobes are smart on design and provide ease of use. And it also bags full marks for using the whole wall and looking seamless.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005823\/built-in-designer-wardrobe.jpg\" alt=\"Built in designer wardrobe for a space-saving, modern and functional bedroom interiors\" class=\"wp-image-5993\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005823\/built-in-designer-wardrobe.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005823\/built-in-designer-wardrobe-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005823\/built-in-designer-wardrobe-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005823\/built-in-designer-wardrobe-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Consider a built-in wardrobe for space-saving, modern and functional bedroom interiors<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Space saving wardrobe solutions with 20% extra space\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/26111224\/Space-saving-wardrobe-solutions-with-20-extra-space-scaled.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>So, whether you are considering a quick revamp or looking at wardrobes for a new home, these designer wardrobes will definitely come in handy before you take the leap. For any further <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/\">interior design<\/a> query, do reach out for a quick consultation and we will be more than happy to help you!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Explore, More About<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/guides\/how-to-choose-wardrobe-for-bedroom\/\">How To Design A Wardrobe For Your Bedroom<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/tv-wardrobe-designs\/\">Latest TV Wardrobe Designs For Your Home<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a 